---
title: Nan's-Spiced Haloumi Burger with Special Burger Sauce & Kumara Wedges
description: Serve up a hearty meat-free burger with a golden "patty" of haloumi that's coated in our popular Nan's special seasoning!
We've added a special burger sauce and oven-baked kumara wedges to turn this easy dinner into a taste sensation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-nans-haloumi-burger-d75314f0.jpg
